      "text": [
        "376 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَنْ مَاتَ مُحْرِماً بَعَثَهُ اَللَّهُ مُلَبِّياً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.376 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whoever dies in the state of Ihram (consecration for Hajj or Umrah), Allah (swt) will resurrect them reciting the Talbiyah.\""
        ]
      }
    }
